#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int isPerfectSquare(long long unsigned int n)
{
    long long unsigned int s=sqrt(n);
    if(n == (s*s))
        return 1;
    else
        return 0;
}
int main()
{
    int t;
    long long unsigned int n;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {
        cin>>n;
        if(isPerfectSquare(5*n*n + 4) || isPerfectSquare(5*n*n - 4))
            cout<<"is fibo"<<endl;
        else
            cout<<"not fibo"<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
